{"tid":2036453,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實應該叫「專重兩制」","createTime":"2020-05-26T12:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T05:16:51.000Z","uid":17831,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7631f2100ef0557a852c663d22be4f5cc1dabd0b","tid":2036453,"uid":17831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:54:54.000Z","msg":"咪比負評先...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係個個都勇武，都唔係個個敢香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政治係要最大共識，要爭取最多香港本地人共識。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果要和理非加入，一定要講清楚而家最大問題係咩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實國安法最大問題，係破壞香港自治既兩制。<br />\n國安法而家點執行，根本連法官律書高官都唔知點做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以往勇武做野一定要有和理非配合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知制度下係唔work,但要聚集最大既聲音，一定要講出香港人合法內既心聲。<br />\n至於勇武想點叫，想點郁，就睇情況啦"},{"pid":"19c73c942bd25ea723055ec1b34744adc13feac5","tid":2036453,"uid":201604,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:57:13.000Z","msg":"你每次為左合法 將自己可以做既野越收越窄<br />\n收細左咁多次 你覺得合法仲有意思？"},{"pid":"394471aa06335a433a860d2274a8e8ce6ead9ffc","tid":2036453,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:58:36.000Z","msg":"唔怪得而家啲學生話中文係死亡之卷<br />\n<br />\n頂你個肺連尊重都唔撚識寫"},{"pid":"29a99fb4ce77f289c50ed7eb3922233459cd6e79","tid":2036453,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:58:44.000Z","msg":"[文長慎入]中共已經｢哂冷｣，香港人選擇下注還是下跪？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2029861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2029861</a>"},{"pid":"053a25e7b630ffe47ef941c72354a8046b574374","tid":2036453,"uid":299171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:59:22.000Z","msg":"條友同支共講尊